                  <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Karan Aujla</h5>
                      <p class="card-text">Karan Aujla, a renowned Punjabi singer and songwriter, has left an indelible mark on the music industry with his distinct voice and impactful lyrics. Known for his versatile style, Aujla's compositions seamlessly blend Punjabi folk with contemporary beats, captivating audiences worldwide. His magnetic stage presence and chart-topping hits have solidified his position as a leading figure in the Punjabi music scene....</p>
